{
  "texts": [
    "Among the delensing models, the cross-spectrum delensing model (L3) produces the smallest biases while maintaining comparable uncertainty on r. Additionally, we conduct a detailed study of the biases introduced by delensing procedure at the power spectra level.",
    "As this paper is focused on the delensing procedure, the whole pipeline is based on the foreground cleaned maps whose foreground residuals are negligible.",
    "1The outline of the paper is as follows: In Section 2, we introduce two delensing methods utilized in our work, followed by a comprehensive analysis of the biases introduced by delensing.",
    "Section 3 provides details of the simulation setup for both the CMB maps and the lensing potential maps.",
    "Our main delensing results are presented in Section 4, alongside a subsequent analysis involving noise debiasing and a comparison of the two delensing methods."
  ]
}